	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Salus et pax Christi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Nec mihi est, quod praeter salutationem ad te scribam<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p495">Bullingers</persName> Brief, auf den <persName ref="p4079">Zwick</persName> antwortet, ist verloren.</note>; est autem salutatio ista communis fratrum omnium, praecipue <persName ref="p8055">Ambrosii</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p8055">Ambrosius Blarer</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="p4082">Cuͦnradi</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p4082">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="p8178">Thomae</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p8178">Thomas Blarer</persName>.</note> consulis nostri.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Omnes cupiunt, ut valeas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Dudum audivi <persName ref="p1039">Euandrum</persName> non mansurum <placeName ref="l907">Campoduni</placeName>; causam<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p1039">Euanders</persName> Stellung in <placeName ref="l907">Kempten</placeName> war durch den Streit der Pfarrer über die Abendmahlslehre bedroht; vgl. unten <ref target="file11289">Nr. 1246</ref>, 15f mit Anm. 6.</note> non audivi nisi iam ex te, et facile crediderim bonum virum isthac permoveri, nec tamen vellem <placeName ref="l907">Campodunensem</placeName> scolam illo privari.<pb type="edition" next="44"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p467">Bucerus</persName> ex <placeName ref="l213">Hassia</placeName> et <placeName ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName> his diebus rediit<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. oben <ref target="file11260">Nr. 1217</ref>, 31f.</note>; quid novi adferat secum, non habemus etiamnum<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>in der Vorlage</hi> etiam nun.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p1753">Leo</persName><note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="p1753">Leo Jud</persName>.</note> nuper michi commendavit <persName ref="p20422">Thomam</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Wohl ein Student; er hielt sich mehrere Monate bei <persName ref="p4079">Zwick</persName> auf und reiste anschließend nach <placeName ref="l558">Wittenberg</placeName>, wo er sich im November 1540 immatrikulierte; s. <bibl>Vadian BW V</bibl> 564; <placeName ref="l558">Wittenberg</placeName>, Matrikel I 188.</note> quendam <placeName ref="l1322">Lovaniensem</placeName>; sed nusquam vidi hominem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">De <persName ref="p4225">Michaele</persName><note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Gemeint ist vielleicht <persName ref="p4225">Michael Back</persName>; vgl. <bibl>HBBW VI</bibl> <ref target="file10899">[Nr. 859]</ref>, S. 356f, Anm. 1.</note> meo nuper scripsi<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10">Ein entsprechender Brief <persName ref="p4079">Zwicks</persName> ist nicht vorhanden.</note> illum in<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>vor</hi> in <hi>gestrichenes</hi> au.</note> <placeName ref="l850">Austria</placeName> bene habere; interim etiam <persName ref="p7604">Khienringius</persName><note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11"><persName ref="p7604">Balthasar von Kuenring</persName>.</note> idem scribit<note xml:id="fn12" type="footnote" n="12">Auch dieser Brief ist nicht erhalten.</note>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">De profectu autem evangelii quid sperandum, cum reges et principes istud persequantur?</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Sed quid dico, quasi vero regnum Christi non proficiat cęsaribus invitis!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Sed vale cum tota domo.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">27. ianuarii 1539.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" ana="salute"><persName ref="p1753">Leonem</persName> salutabis multis modis meo nomine et fac eum certiorem eius, quod hic de <persName ref="p4225">Michaele</persName> scripsi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p4079">Io. Zvick</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Domino <persName ref="p495">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, fratrum charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l587">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
